name: Alter-inventory
tagline: Manage product inventory synchronized with e-commerce with wordpress and woocommerce
body:
### Welcome to Altertech on GitHub Pages.
We open this page to contribute to the big open-source community with us skills and we hope in a big help by the network to complete our big free project:

# Our first project is about woocommerce inventory alternative manager, we have make a plugin worked on Wordpress 3.8.1 and Woocommerce 2.0

```
$ cd http://github.com/bigbabert/alter-inventory
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
